### Get all products (no filters)
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products

### Search by term - "Harry Potter"
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?searchTerm=Harry Potter

### Search by term - "dystopian"
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?searchTerm=dystopian

### Filter by Genre - Fantasy
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?genre=Fantasy

### Filter by Genre - Dystopian Fiction
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?genre=Dystopian Fiction

### Filter by Genre - Young Adult
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?genre=Young Adult

### Filter by Author - J. K. Rowling
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?author=J. K. Rowling

### Filter by Author - Fyodor Dostoevsky
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?author=Fyodor Dostoevsky

### Filter by Author - Suzanne Collins
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?author=Suzanne Collins

### Filter by Price Range - Under $15
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?maxPrice=15

### Filter by Price Range - Over $30
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?minPrice=30

### Filter by Price Range - Between $10 and $20
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?minPrice=10&maxPrice=20

### Combined Filters - Fantasy books under $25
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?genre=Fantasy&maxPrice=25

### Combined Filters - Search "Tolkien" and sort by price (ascending)
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?searchTerm=Tolkien&sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc

### Combined Filters - Young Adult books over $35, sorted by name
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?genre=Young Adult&minPrice=35&sortBy=name

### Sort by Author (A-Z)
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?sortBy=author&sortOrder=asc

### Sort by Author (Z-A)
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?sortBy=author&sortOrder=desc

### Sort by Price (Low to High)
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc

### Sort by Price (High to Low)
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?sortBy=price&sortOrder=desc

### Sort by Genre
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?sortBy=genre&sortOrder=asc

### Advanced - Search "fiction" in Dystopian Fiction genre, price $10-$20, sorted by price
GET http://localhost:5052/api/products?searchTerm=fiction&genre=Dystopian Fiction&minPrice=10&maxPrice=20&sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc
